# VolunteerBridge API Reference

**Base URL:** `https://volunteer-bridge-3.onrender.com`  
**Authentication:** All protected routes require `Authorization: Bearer <token>`

## 1. Authentication
| Method | Endpoint | Action | Example Response (JSON) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register` | Create a new account | `{"message": "User registered successfully", "userId": 12}` |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | Authenticate & get JWT | `{"token": "eyJhbG...", "role": "admin", "id": 1}` |

---

## 2. Project Management
| Method | Endpoint | Action | Example Response (JSON) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/api/projects` | Fetch all projects | `[{"id": 1, "title": "Beach Cleanup", "status": "Active"}]` |
| `POST` | `/api/projects` | Create a new project | `{"id": 5, "title": "Food Drive", "createdAt": "2026-03-20"}` |
| `GET` | `/api/projects/:id` | Get project details | `{"id": 1, "title": "Beach Cleanup", "volunteers": 15}` |

---

## 3. Tasks & Coordination
| Method | Endpoint | Action | Example Response (JSON) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/api/tasks/user/:id` | View my assigned tasks | `[{"task_id": 101, "name": "Sorting", "status": "Pending"}]` |
| `POST` | `/api/tasks/:id/assign`| Assign task to users | `{"message": "Task assigned to 3 volunteers"}` |
| `PUT` | `/api/tasks/:id` | Update task status | `{"task_id": 101, "new_status": "Completed"}` |

---

## 4. Reports & Notifications
| Method | Endpoint | Action | Example Response (JSON) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `GET` | `/api/reports/system` | Get global NGO stats | `{"total_projects": 12, "total_hours": 450}` |
| `GET` | `/api/notifications` | View user alerts | `[{"id": 1, "message": "New project created", "seen": false}]` |

