## 5. Donations
| Method | Endpoint | Action | Example Response (JSON) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `POST` | `/api/donations` | Record a contribution | `{"message": "Donation of $500 recorded", "id": 99}` |
| `GET` | `/api/donations` | List all records | `[{"id": 99, "donor": "Anonymous", "amount": 500}]` |

## 6. Error responses

| Status | Meaning | Example Response |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `401` | Unauthorized | `{"message": "No token, authorization denied"}` |
| `403` | Forbidden | `{"message": "Access denied: Admins only"}` |
| `404` | Not Found | `{"message": "Project not found"}` |




